title: Did Jatt quit shoutcasting or something?
body: I'm catching up on my NA LCS and Phreak keeps mentioning something about Jatt leaving or walking out or something like that and Im just wondering if he quit or what?

replies.body: If you're talking about this last weekend, Jatt & Phreak were casting the first game together & Phreak jokingly kicked Jatt out after he made an incorrect prediction so it was a joke they ran with the whole weekend.
I know its a little late but thanks for clearing that up
hopefully. he didn't understand league enough to shoutcast it.
He played on Dig for awhile during season 2 (might have been S1)
